These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: purple, chestnut
1. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |
| Color   | purple | chestnut |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different nationalities: chinese, russian
1. the russian is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |
| Nationality   | chinese | russian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-3::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: scooter, ship
1. the person driving the scooter is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |   2   |
| Transport   | ship | scooter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-4::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  mechanic, police-officer
1. the police-officer is on the left of the mechanic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |
| Job   | police-officer | mechanic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-5::.
House: townhouse, ranch-style
